@startuml
title Gameplay Edit to Build Sequence

actor User
participant "Editor UI" as UI
participant "Redux Store" as Store
participant "Main IPC" as IPC
participant "Build Service" as Build
participant "Toolchain" as Toolchain

User -> UI : Edit event/asset
UI -> Store : dispatch(updateAction)
Store -> UI : state update/render

User -> UI : Run/Export
UI -> Store : dispatch(buildGame)
Store -> IPC : invoke(build request)
IPC -> Build : start build
Build -> Toolchain : compile/package
Toolchain --> Build : logs + status
Build --> IPC : result
IPC --> Store : build status update
Store --> UI : show success/failure

@enduml
